	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Actually it's not in reference to a song I'm working on. I was just generally surprised to find that macro data is so severely limited (in comparison to note data).
<br />
<br />I guess if it ever becomes a problem, I can just use SM and many many @n commands to achieve the same thing.

		

		</td>
